    "description": "<div style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif;font-size:16px;line-height:1.6;color:#222;max-width:800px;margin:0 auto\" vocab=\"https://schema.org/\" typeof=\"Product\">\n  <div style=\"display:none\"><span property=\"description\">Reveal Your Natural Glow with Vaseline Cocoa Glow Body Cream!</span></div>\n  <div style=\"background:#f5f5f5;padding:12px 15px;border:1px solid #e5e5e5;margin:0 0 16px\">\n    <div style=\"font-size:18px;font-weight:bold;margin-bottom:6px\">Deals Only Web Store</div>\n    <div style=\"font-size:13px\">\n      <a href=\"https://www.ebay.com/str/dealsonlywebstore\" style=\"text-decoration:none;color:#333\">Our Store</a>\n    </div>\n  </div>\n  <h2 style=\"font-size:22px;margin:0 0 12px\">Vaseline 2.53oz Cocoa Glow Body Cream Moisturizizing Lotion (Many Pack Sizes)</h2>\n  <p>Reveal Your Natural Glow with Vaseline Cocoa Glow Body Cream!</p>\n  <h3 style=\"font-size:18px;margin:18px 0 8px\">Key Features</h3>\n  <ul style=\"padding-left:20px;margin:0 0 16px\">\n    <li>DEEPLY MOISTURIZES AND HEALS - Formulated to penetrate deeply and help heal dry, dull skin for a naturally radiant glow.</li>\n    <li>INFUSED WITH COCOA AND SHEA BUTTER - Enriched with nourishing ingredients that soften and smooth skin from within.</li>\n    <li>NON-GREASY, RICH TEXTURE - Luxuriously creamy formula absorbs quickly without leaving residue.</li>\n    <li>CONVENIENT 2.53 OUNCE SIZE - perfect for on-the-go hydration; fits easily in your bag or desk drawer.</li>\n    <li>DAILY GLOW ENHANCER - Ideal for everyday use to restore skin’s softness and leave a lasting, healthy-looking shine.</li>\n  </ul>\n  <p style=\"text-align:center;margin:0 0 16px\"><img src=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/usurper-products/72239/sFsxMKQ1uctSqHF6XgBH5acUMeTCbv-metaODI3ODNfY29jb2FfZ2xvd19vcGVuLmpwZw==-.jpg\" alt=\"Reveal Your Natural Glow with Vaseline Cocoa Glow Body Cream\" style=\"max-width:100%;width:600px;height:auto\"></p>\n  <h3 style=\"font-size:18px;margin:18px 0 8px\">Product Specifications</h3>\n  <ul style=\"padding-left:20px;margin:0 0 16px\">\n    <li><strong>MPN:</strong> 4SNVCGBC1</li>\n    <li><strong>Color:</strong> White</li>\n    <li><strong>Size:</strong> Regular</li>\n  </ul>\n  <p>Say goodbye to dry, dull skin and hello to a soft, radiant glow with Vaseline Cocoa Glow Body Cream. This rich, non-greasy lotion is specially formulated to deeply moisturize and help heal dry skin, bringing out your skin’s natural luminosity with every use.</p>\n  <p>Enriched with Cocoa Butter and Shea Butter, it delivers intense hydration while nourishing your skin from within. The result? Velvety smooth skin that looks and feels healthy, soft, and deeply cared for.</p>\n  <p>Compact and convenient in a 2.53oz size, it’s perfect for your purse, desk, or travel bag—so you can glow up your routine anytime, anywhere. Designed for daily use, this deeply moisturizing lotion restores the skin’s softness and leaves behind a warm, comforting scent that lingers throughout the day.</p>\n  <p style=\"text-align:center;margin:16px 0 0\"><img src=\"https://s3.us-east-1.amazonaws.com/DOWS_photobucket/Shopify_Prop65graphic.jpg\" alt=\"California Proposition 65 warning\" style=\"display:block;margin-left:auto;margin-right:auto\" height=\"78\" width=\"273\"></p>\n  <p style=\"margin:18px 0 0;padding-top:12px;border-top:1px solid #e5e5e5;font-size:13px;color:#777;text-align:center\">&copy; 2026 Deals Only Web Store</p>\n</div>",
